  <entry>
    <title>Jenkins图文详细安装教程</title>
    <url>/2020/05/03/Jenkins%E5%9B%BE%E6%96%87%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%99%E7%A8%8B/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="一、安装jdk"><a href="#一、安装jdk" class="headerlink" title="一、安装jdk"></a>一、安装jdk</h2><p><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1Yfeh8V4lz3nI4gwXOkx-4A" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jdk</a></p>
<p><strong>提取码</strong>：545u</p>
<p><strong>1.上传或下载安装包</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd/usr/local   (将安装包放在目录下)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1urhFX_OB_UkBvvRFNN713A" target="_blank" rel="noopener">xftp</a></p>
<p><strong>提取码</strong>：gewq</p>
<blockquote>
<p>可使用xftp进行传输文件</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>2.解压安装包</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -zxvf jdk-<span class="number">8</span>u161-linux-x64.tar</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>3.修改环境变量</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/profile</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">export JAVA_HOME=/usr/local/jdk</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">export JRE_HOME=$JAVA_HOME/jre</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">export CLASSPATH=.:$CLASSPATH:$JAVA_HOME/lib:$JRE_HOME/lib</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">export PATH=$PATH:$JAVA_HOME/bin:$JRE_HOME/bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">source /etc/profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>通过命令source /etc/profile让profile文件立即生效</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>4.测试是否jdk安装成功</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">java -version</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>出现版本号及成功。</p>
<h2 id="二、安装Maven"><a href="#二、安装Maven" class="headerlink" title="二、安装Maven"></a>二、安装Maven</h2><p><strong>1. 上传或下载安装包</strong><br><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/11ZvwmKx2JsO9BC9WOVTXGQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Maven</a></p>
<p>提取码：o51k</p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd/usr/local  (将安装包放在目录下)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>2. 解压安装包</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -zxvf apache-maven-<span class="number">3.6</span><span class="number">.3</span>-bin.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>3. 修改环境变量</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/profile</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">export MAVEN_HOME=/usr/local/apache-maven-<span class="number">3.6</span><span class="number">.3</span></span><br><span class="line">export PATH=$MAVEN_HOME/bin:$PATH</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">通过命令source /etc/profile让profile文件立即生效</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">source /etc/profile</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200503184309833.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"><br><strong>4. 测试是否安装成功</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mvn –v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200503184411742.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<h2 id="三、安装git"><a href="#三、安装git" class="headerlink" title="三、安装git"></a>三、安装git</h2><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum -y install git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="四、安装Docker"><a href="#四、安装Docker" class="headerlink" title="四、安装Docker"></a>四、安装Docker</h2><p><strong>1. 安装必要的一些系统工具</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum install -y yum-utils device-mapper-persistent-data lvm2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>2. 添加软件源信息</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum-config-manager --add-repo http:<span class="comment">//mirrors.aliyun.com/docker-ce/linux/centos/docker-ce.repo</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p> <strong>3. 更新并安装Docker-CE</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum makecache fast</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">yum -y install docker-ce</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p> <strong>4. 开启Docker服务</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service docker start</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>5. 测试是否安装成功</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200503184830822.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<h2 id="五、安装Jenkins"><a href="#五、安装Jenkins" class="headerlink" title="五、安装Jenkins"></a>五、安装Jenkins</h2><p><a href="https://pan.baidu.com/s/1lrmzoLQHpn9_8sPg9zj58w" target="_blank" rel="noopener">jenkins</a></p>
<p><strong>提取码</strong>：jfrh </p>
<blockquote>
<p>采用war包安装方式</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>1. 上传文件</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd/usr/local  (将安装包放在目录下)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">mkdir jenkins</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">cd jenkins/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>2. 启动</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">nohup java -jar  /usr/local/jenkins/jenkins.war &gt;/usr/local/jenkins/jenkins.out &amp;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200503190303144.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>按两次空格</p>
</blockquote>
<p><strong>3. 访问</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http:<span class="comment">//ip(自己的ip地址):8080</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">访问失败的要开放<span class="number">8080</span>端口</span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd --zone=<span class="keyword">public</span> --add-port=<span class="number">8080</span>/tcp --permanent</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">firewall-cmd --reload (重启防火墙生效)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2020050319154088.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2xsbGxsbGtra2trb29vb28=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<p><strong>获取管理员密码</strong><br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/2020050318560229.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<p><strong>4.     看到这一步，先不要点安装，关闭浏览器，配置国内镜像</strong><br><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200503185705668.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L2xsbGxsbGtra2trb29vb28=,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<p><strong>4.1  结束jenkins进程</strong></p>
<p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20200503190447612.png" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p>
<p><strong>4.2 进入updates目录配置镜像</strong></p>
